lead_paragraph: Gavin Floyd pitched three strong innings and prospect Darrell Ceciliani hit a long grand slam, leading the Toronto Blue Jays past a Minnesota Twins split squad 9-3 on Tuesday.

headline.main: Floyd Solid, Blue Jays Beat Twins Split Squad 9-3
